<p><strong>Medium humanoid (human, shapechanger), neutral good</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 10 (in humanoid form, 11 in bear and hybrid forms )</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 135 (18d8+54)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft. (40 ft., climb 30 ft. in bear or hybrid form)</p>

